fields.name: Valete
fields.bio_summary: Valete is a Portuguesehip hop artist named Keidje Lima from Benfica, Lisbon.

fields.name: Logic
fields.bio_summary: Sir Robert Bryson Hall II (born January 22, 1990), known by his stage name Logic, is an American rapper from Gaithersburg, Maryland.

fields.name: Sobre
fields.bio_summary: Sobre is a french rapper from Caen. He is a member of the 1treuk crew.

fields.name: Main Attrakionz
fields.bio_summary: Main Attrakionz is an American hip hop duo from Oakland, California, composed of rappers Mondre M.A.N. (Damondre Grice) and Squadda B (Charles Glover).

fields.name: Furax Barbossa
fields.bio_summary: Furax also know as Furax Barbarossa, is a french rapper from Toulouse. he was a member of the Polychrome 7 crew.

fields.name: Youssef Swatt's
fields.bio_summary: Youssef Swatt's is a Belgian rapper from Tournai.

fields.name: Rae Sremmurd
fields.bio_summary: Rae Sremmurd is an American hip hop duo originating from Tupelo, Mississippi formed by Swae Lee and Slim Jxmmi. The group is best know for their hit Black Beatles.

fields.name: La caution
fields.bio_summary: La Caution is a French hip hop duo consisting of members Hi-Tekk and Nikkfurie of Moroccan descent.

fields.name: Timbaland
fields.bio_summary: Timothy Zachery "Tim" Mosley (born March 10, 1972), known professionally as Timbaland, is an American record producer, singer, songwriter, rapper and DJ.

fields.name: Goodie Mob
fields.bio_summary: Goodie Mob is a hip hop group based in Atlanta, Georgia that formed in 1991 and currently consists of members Cee-Lo, Khujo, T-Mo, and Big Gipp. The group is part of the Dungeon Family collective.
